import React from 'react'; import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next'; import { useQuery } from 'react-query'; import apiService from '../services/apiService'; import LoadingSpinner from '../components/LoadingSpinner'; const FieldOfficerDashboard = () => { const { t } = useTranslation(); const { data: stats, isLoading: statsLoading } = useQuery( 'fieldOfficerStats', apiService.getDashboardStats ); const { data: distributions, isLoading: distributionsLoading } = useQuery( 'distributions', apiService.getDistributions ); if (statsLoading || distributionsLoading) return ; return (

{t('fieldOfficerDashboard')}

{/* Stats Cards */}
{t('assignedProjects')}
{stats?.assigned_projects || 0}
{t('distributionsRecorded')}
{stats?.distributions_recorded || 0}
{t('reportsSubmitted')}
{stats?.reports_submitted || 0}
{/* Quick Actions */}

{t('recordDistribution')}

{t('recordDistributionDesc')}

{t('submitReport')}

{t('submitReportDesc')}

{/* Recent Distributions */}

{t('recentDistributions')}

{distributions?.results?.map((distribution) => ( ))}
{t('project')} {t('aidType')} {t('beneficiaries')} {t('date')} {t('status')}
{distribution.project_title} {distribution.aid_type} {distribution.beneficiaries_count} {new Date(distribution.distribution_date).toLocaleDateString()} {distribution.is_verified ? t('verified') : t('pending')}
); }; export default FieldOfficerDashboard;
